txt.en: Wraiths can be found in Emyn Duir.\n\nYou should defeat wraiths, vengeful and otherwise, that plague the land.
A bounty notice asks you to clear wraiths from around Emyn Duir.
You have defeated wraiths around Emyn Duir hopefully putting an end to the haunting of the land. Whether this will end the stories that so bothered the man who posted the bounty remains to be seen.

The bounty notice reads:

'Shivers and screams in the night! A terrible, lingering presence! Cold, chilling wind, blowing suddenly from nowhere! These are only some of the stories my men have told to me, trying to convince me that these lands are haunted. It begins to interfere with their patrols, which means it must stop, and now!

'Put an end to the wraiths, and you will put an end to the stories, and earn some coin beside.'
Defeat vengeful wraiths in Emyn Duir ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
